snippet.title: Starfield Full Presentation | Gamescom ONL 2023
snippet.description:
Gamescom ONL 2023 kicked everything off with an all new live action trailer for Bethesda's next big RPG, Starfield. Todd Howard took the stage to hype up the highly anticipated game, including audience members who rushed the stage to mutter something about GTA 6.

Timestamps
0:00 Starfield Live Action Trailer
2:11 Random Fan Interruption
3:10 Todd Howard Talks Starfield

To learn more about how to pre-order Starfield and its various accessories check out our pre-order guide at https://www.gamespot.com/articles/starfield-preorder-guide/1100-6515113/
